author: National Geographic
description:
Vikings would run towards death without fear—a legacy that Ken Stornes continues. Can David Blaine rise to the challenge and death dive with the same determination?

Find out in David Blaine: Do Not Attempt, tonight at 9/8c on National Geographic. Episodes 3 and 4 are now streaming on Disney+ and Hulu.
title: How will @DavidBlaine handle death-diving? #DavidBlaineDoNotAttempt

description:
